    <briefdescription>
<para>Specialized modules extending AnalysisG functionality. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The Modules directory contains specialized components that extend the framework&apos;s capabilities. Each module provides specific functionality for physics analysis, machine learning, data handling, and utility operations.</para>
<sect1 id="group__modules__group_1modules_structure">
<title>Module Structure</title>
<para>Each module follows a consistent directory structure:</para>
<para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal">module_name/</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">├──<sp/>CMakeLists.txt<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>#<sp/>Build<sp/>configuration</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">├──<sp/>include/<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>#<sp/>Header<sp/>files</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">│<sp/><sp/><sp/>└──<sp/>templates/<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>#<sp/>Template<sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">class<sp/></highlight><highlight class="normal">headers</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">│<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>└──<sp/>module.h</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">└──<sp/>cxx/<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>#<sp/>Implementation<sp/>files</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>└──<sp/>module.cxx</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</sect1>
